Program: Outlook
Title: A Nightmare in Wonderland
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/w3cswt6t
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 3 Dec 2018
Travel writer Claire Nelson was hiking in Joshua Tree, California when she slipped off a boulder and fell 15ft into a canyon. She was trapped, and completely alone in the scorching hot wilderness, with limited water. How would she survive? Presenter: Emily Webb Producer: Maryam Maruf Image: Joshua Tree Credit: Ernst Haas/Getty Images Show less